            "description": "Two-loop planar double box contributing to Higgs+jet production through a massive quark loop. Three dimensionless parameters. 72 master integrals (reduced from 73 by a new Kira 2.0 relation). Elliptic subsector (pinched propagator 3) with 4 masters. Four new functions $G_1,...,G_4$ are needed: $G_1,G_2$ for the homogeneous elliptic system, $G_3,G_4$ for the inhomogeneous contributions from subtopologies. All $G_i$ are integrals of $\\varpi_0$ times rational/algebraic functions over the mass variable.",
